01:52:27.116 --> 01:52:28.106 A:middle
Next, I want to turn to some

01:52:28.106 --> 01:52:30.006 A:middle
great enhancements to Safari.

01:52:30.406 --> 01:52:31.756 A:middle
Safari works really hard to

01:52:32.296 --> 01:52:33.856 A:middle
protect your privacy, and this

01:52:33.856 --> 01:52:35.736 A:middle
year it's working even harder.

01:52:36.116 --> 01:52:37.856 A:middle
Last year, we introduced

01:52:37.856 --> 01:52:39.556 A:middle
intelligent tracking prevention

01:52:39.916 --> 01:52:41.546 A:middle
to dramatically reduce the

01:52:41.546 --> 01:52:43.456 A:middle
ability for apps to track you

01:52:43.456 --> 01:52:45.486 A:middle
across websites using cookies.

01:52:46.626 --> 01:52:47.566 A:middle
This is the kind of thing where

01:52:47.566 --> 01:52:48.946 A:middle
