01:52:48.946 --> 01:52:49.306 A:middle
site.

01:52:49.656 --> 01:52:51.106 A:middle
Then you move to another site

01:52:51.376 --> 01:52:53.096 A:middle
and another site and somehow

01:52:53.096 --> 01:52:54.156 A:middle
this is just following you

01:52:54.156 --> 01:52:55.286 A:middle
wherever you go.

